MINI PROJECT 1: 2048 Game
In this assignment, I have created implementation of the 2048 game. It is a simple grid based game , in which we have to make 2048 number by combining blocks with same number.

MINI PROJECT 2: TIC TAC TOE BY Monte Carlo Method
In this assignment, I have implemented a machine player for Tic-Tac-Toe. Machine player will use a Monte Carlo simulation to decide its next move.


